Launch windows server

Go to server manager 
Click on Add Roles and features
Click next >> select Role based feature based installation  then click next
In server selection choose default ‘select server from the server pool’  click next  In Server Role session select Webserver(IIS), then click Add features and click next.
Click on Next till The Installation
After the installation IIS will be available in Server Manager
====
Click on services in IIS click on Go To IIS
